" get summary on this repository
nnoremap <silent> <leader>gg :<C-u>Git<CR>

" git blame
nnoremap <silent> <leader>gb :<C-u>Git blame<CR>
xnoremap <silent> <leader>gb :Git blame<CR>

" git log
nnoremap <silent> <leader>gl :<C-u>Gclog %<CR>
xnoremap <silent> <leader>gl :Gclog<CR>
nnoremap <silent> <leader>gL :<C-u>Gclog<CR>

" git diff
nnoremap <silent> <leader>gd :<C-u>Git diff<CR>
